joosjidiiozkgodsxqgcbiembodehmvcgcxqvmxe length 5 76881 page 76881 <!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><title>Climate Change Is Making India's Monsoon More Erratic</title><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta content="IE=Edge" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=10.0,user-scalable=yes,minimum-scale=1.0"><meta name="description" content="Marked by extreme localised rainfall events, an unusually dry August and an unusually wet September, the summer monsoon in 2021 kept India guessing, even on its way out. Expect more of the same in future, say climate change assessments"><meta name="application-name" content="Indiaspend"><meta name="keywords" content="climate change, agriculture, monsoon, summer, heavy rainfall, environment,"><meta name="news_keywords" content="climate change, agriculture, monsoon, summer, heavy rainfall, environment,"><meta name="language" content="en"><meta name="google" content="notranslate"><meta name="author" content="Tanvi Deshpande"><meta name="copyright" content="Indiaspend"><meta name="robots" content="follow, index"><meta name="robots" content="max-image-preview:large"><meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="true"><meta name="referrer" content="origin"><meta name="twitter:site" content="@IndiaSpend"><meta name="twitter:creator" content="@IndiaSpend"><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.indiaspend.com/earthcheck/climate-change-is-making-indias-monsoon-more-erratic-780356"><meta name="twitter:url" content="https://www.indiaspend.com/earthcheck/climate-change-is-making-indias-monsoon-more-erratic-780356"><meta name="title" content="Climate Change Is Making India's Monsoon More Erratic"><meta name="image" content="https://www.indiaspend.com/h-upload/2021/10/11/572350-cover-indias-monsoon-is-getting-more-erratic1600.jpg"><meta name="original-source" content="https://www.indiaspend.com/earthcheck/climate-change-is-maki